Juncker Says Fiscal Stimulus Packages in Europe Not Possible

-- B y   J a m e s   H e r t l i n g
-- 
2011-09-16T11:19:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/juncker-says-fiscal-stimulus-packages-in-europe-not-possible.html
Luxembourg Prime Minister Jean-
Claude Juncker, who heads the group of euro-area finance
ministers, said the demands of budget cutting make any plan to
spur growth through fiscal measures impossible. He spoke after a
meeting of euro finance chiefs today in Wroclaw,  Poland .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Hertling at 
 jhertling@bloomberg.net  